  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div data-tool=\"markdown编辑器\" data-website=\"https://markdown.com.cn/editor\" style=\"font-size: 16px;padding: 25px 30px;word-spacing: 0px;word-break: break-word;word-wrap: break-word;text-align: justify;margin-top: -10px;line-height: 1.75;color: #595959;font-family: Optima-Regular, Optima, PingFangTC-Light, PingFangSC-light, PingFangTC-light;letter-spacing: 2px;background-image: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(50, 0, 0, 0.05) 3%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 3%), linear-gradient(360deg, rgba(50, 0, 0, 0.05) 3%, rgba(0, 0, 0, 0) 3%);background-size: 20px 20px;background-position: center center;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\">\n   <blockquote style=\"border:1px solid #DEC6FB;padding-top:10px;text-size-adjust:100%;color:#595959;font-weight:400;display:block;padding-left:20px;font-size:0.9em;padding-bottom:10px;line-height:1.55em;font-style:normal;box-sizing:inherit;overflow-scrolling:touch;border-radius:6px;overflow:auto;border-left:none;margin-top:20px;margin-bottom:20px;padding-right:10px;text-align:left;\">\n    <span style=\"font-weight:700;font-size:34px;line-height:1;\"><span leaf=\"\">❝</span></span>\n    <p style=\"padding-top: 8px;padding-bottom: 8px;letter-spacing: 2px;font-size: 14px;word-spacing: 2px;margin: 0px;line-height: 26px;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">VS Code 之所以成为最受欢迎的编辑器之一，很大程度上得益于其丰富的扩展生态。本人精选 20 个实用 or 有趣的 VS Code 扩展，覆盖摸鱼放松，文件管理、代码规范、效率工具等等多个场景，干货满满，下面正片开始：</span></p>\n    <span style=\"float:right;\"><span leaf=\"\">❞</span></span>\n   </blockquote>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;padding-left: 10px;border-left: 5px solid #DEC6FB;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">1 看小说漫画：any-reader</span></span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「核心功能」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">： 在 VS Code 中阅读小说、文档，支持 TXT/EPUB 格式、章节导航、字体调整。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「适用场景」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：利用碎片时间阅读技术文档或轻小说，避免频繁切换应用。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「隐藏技巧」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：支持自定义快捷键翻页，可设置阅读定时提醒。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <figure data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin: 0;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100062616\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.5546296296296296\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: auto;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 20px auto;object-fit: contain;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=b0d86325&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FlCQLg02gtibusRpu0cPeLsw5u9w1ZWXPrMzZrZBEVv8ky2TP95D8icfibIbIibHX080tOnM0IGSGkgWgib8eTHHnwcw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;padding-left: 10px;border-left: 5px solid #DEC6FB;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">2 偷偷在状态栏看小说：Thief-Book</span></span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「核心功能」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：在状态栏显示小说，支持阅读进度。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「适用场景」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：利用碎片时间阅读技术文档或轻小说，避免频繁切换应用。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「隐藏技巧」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：支持快捷键翻页。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <figure data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin: 0;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100062613\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.1788793103448276\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"464\" style=\"width: auto;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 20px auto;object-fit: contain;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=868f5bc2&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FlCQLg02gtibusRpu0cPeLsw5u9w1ZWXPrFWMr5FTv2WOLuc7nHUkSQrglMHVZaM2sudtgPXdyPOP1AicVhQyUAZA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;padding-left: 10px;border-left: 5px solid #DEC6FB;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">3 看股票基金期货：韭菜盒子</span></span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「核心功能」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: square;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">基金实时涨跌，实时数据，支持海外基展示</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">股票实时涨跌，支持 A 股、港股、美股</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">期货实时涨跌，支持国内期货</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">底部状态栏信息</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">开市自动刷新，节假日关闭轮询</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持升序 / 降序排序、基金持仓金额升序 / 降序</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">基金实时走势图和历史走势图</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">基金排行榜</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">基金持仓信息</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">支持维护持仓成本价，自动计算收益率</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">基金趋势统计图</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">基金支持分组展示等等...</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「注意：投资有风险，入市需谨慎！」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100062615\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.0899182561307903\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"734\" style=\"width: auto;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 20px auto;object-fit: contain;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=83d92887&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FlCQLg02gtibusRpu0cPeLsw5u9w1ZWXPrbpKnEYq6qtKlmrjOY4iaAddYU6TnuFWreKAXK0fiaktIiaYIibqT5hvvlQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;padding-left: 10px;border-left: 5px solid #DEC6FB;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">4 小霸王</span></span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「核心功能」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：一款基于 vscode 的 nes 游戏插件，主打本地与远程游戏资源管理，让你在编辑器内就能完成游戏的添加、下载、启动全流程。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「不建议上班玩哈！」</span></strong></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <figure data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin: 0;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100062614\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.47162790697674417\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"1075\" style=\"width: auto;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 20px auto;object-fit: contain;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=0b5e55c6&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FlCQLg02gtibusRpu0cPeLsw5u9w1ZWXPrdhbnSvWnTrNLo1ItEhp2buvAcVDL4VMAAGmWNib54iaxCLj02xeDeyNA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;font-weight:bold;font-size:22px;margin-top:30px;margin-bottom:15px;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"display: none;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;font-weight: bold;display: inline-block;padding-left: 10px;border-left: 5px solid #DEC6FB;color: #595959;\"><span leaf=\"\">5 JSON 变可视化树图：JSON Crack</span></span></h2>\n   <ul style=\"margin-top: 8px;margin-bottom: 8px;padding-left: 25px;font-size: 15px;color: #595959;list-style-type: circle;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「核心功能」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：将 JSON 数据转换为交互式树状可视化图表，支持折叠 / 展开节点、搜索内容。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「适用场景」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：分析复杂 JSON 结构（如 API 响应、配置文件）、快速定位数据层级。</span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     <p style=\"margin-top: 5px;margin-bottom: 5px;line-height: 26px;text-align: left;font-size: 14px;font-weight: normal;color: #595959;\"><strong style=\"color: #595959;font-weight: bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">「优势」</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：比原生 JSON 格式化更直观，支持大体积 JSON 数据渲染。</span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <figure data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin: 0;margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;\">\n    <span leaf=\"\"><img data-imgfileid=\"100062612\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.559463986599665\" data-type=\"other\" data-w=\"597\" style=\"width: auto;max-width: 100%;border-radius: 6px;display: block;margin: 20px auto;object-fit: contain;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=215c5641&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_jpg%2FlCQLg02gtibusRpu0cPeLsw5u9w1ZWXPriavmiaRqkOgbwklQAo0n2SiciciaoPAk0qJofsSHc6bI2OompBQiat2KnNgQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dother%26from%3Dappmsg\"></span>\n   </figure>\n   <h2 data-tool=\"markdown.com.cn编辑器\" style=\"margin:20px 10px 0px 0px;f